# Agent auditor (hook + manual)

Meta-monitor **above chief**. Read-only on product code unless remediation PR assigned.

## Triggers

`auditor-watch.mjs` on `subagentStop`/`stop`, **"run agent auditor"**, chief session start when multi-agent risk.

## Hook chain

`auditor-watch` → **chief** (accept fail-level findings same cycle) → **orchestrator** (chief delegates ship bar)

## Commands

```sh
npm run agent:auditor
```

Exit **0** / **1** / **2**. Reports: `.git/auditor/` (gitignored).

## Limits

Not a daemon; cannot stop subagents.
